OL,3,CWestminster committee urges Government
OL,4,Cto formally name Stakeknife
OL,6,FA Westminster committee has urged the
OL,7,FGovernment to formally name the former
OL,8,Fagent known as Stakeknife.
OL,10,FThe Army's former spy within the IRA
OL,11,Fduring the Troubles was widely
OL,12,Fbelieved to be west Belfast man
OL,13,FFreddie Scappaticci, who was 77 when
OL,14,Fhe died in 2023.
