OL,3,CWestminster committee urges Government
OL,4,Cto formally name Stakeknife
OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland Affairs Committee
OL,7,Fjoined that call in a report published
OL,8,Fon Monday.
OL,10,FThe MPs from across a number of
OL,11,Fparties concluded that revealing the
OL,12,Fidentity of Stakeknife would be
OL,13,F"strongly in the public interest".
OL,15,FThey also contend it would "help build
OL,16,Ftrust and confidence in the agencies
OL,17,Fof the state among all communities".
