OL,3,CWestminster committee urges Government
OL,4,Cto formally name Stakeknife
OL,6,FIt comes after the committee held an
OL,7,Fevidence session on Operation Kenova
OL,8,Flast month, during which it heard from
OL,9,FSir Iain and Mr Boutcher.
OL,11,FThe report said the committee has been
OL,12,Freassured that formal identification
OL,13,Fwould not put any active agents at
OL,14,Frisk, discourage existing agents from
OL,15,Fcontinuing their work, or deter the
OL,16,Frecruitment of new agents.
