OL,3,CWestminster committee urges Government
OL,4,Cto formally name Stakeknife
OL,6,FIt also contends that naming
OL,7,FStakeknife would also indicate to
OL,8,Fagents guilty of conduct beyond
OL,9,Facceptable limits that they will not
OL,10,Fbe protected or shielded from the
OL,11,Fconsequences of their actions.
OL,13,FCommittee chairwoman Tonia Antoniazzi
OL,14,Fsaid refusing to name Stakeknife is
OL,15,Fhaving an impact on their victims.
