OL,3,CWestminster committee urges Government
OL,4,Cto formally name Stakeknife
OL,6,F"As Operation Kenova's final report
OL,7,Fmakes clear, the ongoing refusal to
OL,8,Fconfirm or deny Stakeknife's identity
OL,9,Fis having a profound and lasting
OL,10,Feffect on victims and their families
OL,11,Fwho have already been through so
OL,12,Fmuch," she said.
OL,14,F"Given the reassurances we've heard
OL,15,Fthat active agents won't be put in
OL,16,Fharm's way and future recruitment
OL,17,Fwon't be compromised, formal
OL,18,Fidentification in this specific
OL,19,Finstance is appropriate, proportionate
OL,20,Fand in the public interest.
