OL,3,CWestminster committee urges Government
OL,4,Cto formally name Stakeknife
OL,6,F"By naming Stakeknife, the Government
OL,7,Fcan send a strong signal that agents
OL,8,Fwho cross a line will not receive the
OL,9,Fprotection of anonymity and help to
OL,10,Fbuild trust and confidence across all
OL,11,Fcommunities in Northern Ireland."
OL,13,FThe committee has recommended that the
OL,14,FGovernment should review, in
OL,15,Fconsultation with MI5 and the PSNI,
OL,16,Fthe application of NCND in all legacy-
OL,17,Frelated cases, considering
OL,18,Fspecifically the principles outlined
OL,19,Fin this report.
