OL,3,CWestminster committee urges Government
OL,4,Cto formally name Stakeknife
OL,6,F"The committee recommendation supports
OL,7,Fthe findings of the Operation Kenova
OL,8,Freport, which included that Stakeknife
OL,9,Fshould be named with a specific
OL,10,Frecommendation for a review of the UK
OL,11,FGovernment policy on its neither
OL,12,Fconfirm nor deny (NCND) policy as it
OL,13,Fis applied to cases that occurred
OL,14,Fduring the Troubles in Northern
OL,15,FIreland," Mr Boutcher said.
OL,17,F"The application of NCND must not be
OL,18,Fallowed to cover up acts of wrongdoing
OL,19,Fby the state. I am grateful for the
OL,20,Fcommittee taking such care in
OL,21,Fexamining this matter."
