OL,6,FA UK Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"The behaviour described in Operation
OL,8,FKenova's final report is deeply
OL,9,Fdisturbing."It should not have
OL,10,Fhappened, and in recent decades, there
OL,11,Fhave been significant reforms to agent
OL,12,Fhandling practice, including through
OL,13,Flegislation.
OL,15,F"The use of agents is nowadays subject
OL,16,Fto strict regulation, overseen by the
OL,17,FInvestigatory Powers Commissioner and
OL,18,Fthe Investigatory Powers Tribunal.
